Introduction: 

Components tests for joke_machine.py, the majority of tests are unit test, since it covers major paths these are the remaining pieces from the joke_machine.py

Getting Started:

1. pip install -r requirements.txt
2. inside the component_tests folder type 'pytest' to run all unit tests.

Following are the component tests:

    test_jm_cli_parser.py - these tests focus on argument_parser tests
    test_jm_error_handler.py - these tests forcus on error_handler tests
    test_joke_machine_class.py - these tests focus to test the class